.DT
facing
Discworld player help
facing

.SH Name
.SI 5
facing - What direction you are currently facing
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
facing
facing <living>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
The facing command can be used to determine what direction you
are currently facing.  In some locations it might not be possible
to determine what direction you are facing unless you have a
point of reference.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> facing
You are facing north.
> facing frog and warriors
Six warriors are facing east and a postal frog is facing north.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
turn, look
.EI
